<p>
Click to launch English version:
<ul>
<li><a href="glaciers.jnlp">Glaciers</a>
</ul>
<p>
<b>What's new:</b>
<p>
<ul>
<li>clean up ground/snow interface for x<0
<li>implement strip charts for time-based graphs, 1000-year window
<li>show both ablation (solid green) and negative ablation (dashed green) on "glacial budget vs elevation" graph
<li>replace "glacier picture" check box with a button
<li>implement Save/Load feature
<li>simplify implementation of snowfall visualization
<li>phetcommon fix for gradients on Mac OS 10.4 (Unfuddle #553), applies to snowfall visualization
<li>fix snowfall visualization so that you don't see blue sky above snow when window is maximized on large monitors
</ul>
<p>
<b>Known problems:</b>
<ul>
<li>full-size background image is so large that it exceeds JVM heap space and causes OutOfMemoryException
<li>glacier starts up in steady state, but with no debris or ripple in the ice, and no moraine
</ul>
<p>
<b>Not implemented:</b>
<ul>
<li>Experiments tab
<li>English/metric units control
<li>Help
</ul>
